{"tid":778657,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"如果想進階學電結他，各位有冇邊個好老師推介？","createTime":"2018-08-14T00:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T22:40:11.000Z","uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcd9060f6babc8779215162415d34f26914008c","tid":778657,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:50:57.000Z","msg":"講番少少自己嘅背景先，<br />\n接觸結他已有十年，但係唔算認真學過。 <br />\n(喺D屋邨琴行學過三四年，之後跟blackwine 個micheal 學咗幾個月就因為有事而未能再學，而家想學番都好，佢都好似無再教了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其餘時間都係自己鳩撩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己目前嘅能力：<br />\n1. 算係彈到《highway star》(我知首野係好初階<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n2. 只係識睇六線譜<br />\n3. 樂理知識近乎零 (只知一個major scale 係「全全半全全全半」，至於chord progression一竅不通)<br />\n4. ear training 近乎零 (聽一首普通流行曲，執唔番個chord)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人到咗三十歲，忽然想認真做 / 學一件事，<br />\n而且見到而家通街嘅人都識彈malmsteen、dream theater 嘅歌，真係令自己好自卑，<br />\n所以好想認真學番結他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想學嘅係：<br />\na. 彈到malmsteen、dream theater 嗰種程度嘅速彈<br />\nb. 即興jam野<br />\nc. 基本樂理 (chord progression 同埋點樣對應番落licks 嘅運用)<br />\nd. funky 嘅節奏結他彈法 (我知配合埋a&mdash;c 三點，呢點係有D雜)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位大佬有冇邊個結他老師可以推薦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(喺fb 最近見到唔少結他老師開page出課金廣告，而睇過佢地嘅片後我無乜信心；之前試過膽粗粗問blaster個結他佬跟佢學，但之後無回音了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"974d50827aa98287abb294cd52bb9bfd96d34d94","tid":778657,"uid":96056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/ycwdan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fycwdan&d=WU70cn3kxO7zAgzGaBbBPYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=be196cd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ycwdan</a><br />\n<br />\n可以tg我傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj